{"id":769732655,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"10 months, 1 week","timestamp":1660084794,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"26 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/769732655/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"58.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        int[] subAt = new int[s.length()];//this stores the longest substring that ends at I\n        if(s.length() == 0)\n            return(0);\n        subAt[0] = 1;\n        int curStart = 0;\n        int max = 1;\n        for(int i = 1; i < s.length(); i++)\n        {\n            //boolean add = true;\n            for(int j = curStart; j < i; j++)\n            {\n                if(s.substring(j, j+1).equals(s.substring(i, i+1)))\n                {    \n                    curStart = j + 1;\n                    break;\n                }\n            }\n            subAt[i] = i - curStart + 1;\n            if (subAt[i] > max)\n                max = subAt[i];\n        }\n        return(max);\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false}
